---
title: Cheesy Capsicum Chicken Melts with Roasted Veggies & Garlic Butter Broccoli
description: Load up chicken breasts with flavour before baking them until golden and tender. Chargrilled capsicum
relish and melted Cheddar combine to make a sensational topping that everyone will happily devour!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
